  "description": "The image captures a cascading waterfall flowing down a rocky cliff face. The waterfall appears narrow and ribbon-like, with water tumbling over multiple tiers and rocky outcrops. The surrounding landscape is dominated by lush green vegetation, primarily trees and shrubs clinging to the steep slopes of the cliff. The cliff face itself is composed of gray rock formations. In the foreground, blurred yellow foliage partially obscures the view, creating a sense of depth. There is a sense of natural wildness and rugged terrain.",
